raft}}, {{ill|Higashimuro District|ja|東牟婁郡|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nachikatsuura Town|ja|那智勝浦町|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Onda Shrine|ja|穏田神社|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Tokyo Metropolis|ja|東京都|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Shibuya Ward|ja|渋谷区|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Jingumae|ja|神宮前 (渋谷区)|12=draft|12=draft}}) * {{ill|Sixth Heavenly Deity Shrine|ja|第六天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Miyagi Prefecture|ja|宮城県|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Natori City|ja|名取市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Masuda) == Footnotes == {{Footnote Help}} === Sources === <references/> == Bibliography == * {{Cite book|Japanese |title=Kojiki |date=December 18, 2007 |publisher={{ill|Iwanami Shoten|ja|岩波書店|12=draft|12=draft}} |ref={{SfnRef|Kurano|2007}} |author={{ill|Kenji Kurano|ja|倉野憲司|12=draft|12=draft}} (annotated) |series={{ill|Iwanami Bunko|ja|岩波文庫|12=draft|12=draft}} |isbn=4-00-300011-0 |edition=Revised}} * {{Cite book|Japanese |title=Shinto Dictionary |date=May 15, 1999 |publisher={{ill|Koubundou|ja|弘文堂|12=draft|12=draft}} |ref={{SfnRef|Nakayama|1999}} |author=Nakayama Iku |editor={{ill|Kokugakuin University|ja|國學院大學|12=draft|12=draft}} Japan Culture Research Institute |edition=Reprint |chapter=Omotaru / Ayakashikone |isbn=4-335-16033-X}} * {{Cite book|Japanese |title=Kojiki |date=October 30, 2014 |publisher={{ill|Shinchosha|ja|新潮社|12=draft|12=draft}} |ref={{SfnRef|Nishimiya|2014}} |author={{ill|Kazuminishi Nishimiya|ja|西宮一民|12=draft|12=draft}} (annotated) |isbn=978-4-10-620801-0 |series={{ill|Shincho Nippon Classical Collection|ja|新潮日本古典集成|12=draft|12=draft}} (New Edition)}} == Related Articles == * {{ill|Creation of Heaven and Earth|ja|天地開闢|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|List of Japanese Deities|ja|日本の神の一覧|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Genealogy of Japanese Deities|ja|日本の神の家系図|12=draft|12=draft}} == External Links == * [https://kojiki.kokugakuin.ac.jp/shinmei/omodarunokami/ Omotaru-no-Kami – Kokugakuin University, Classical Culture Studies] * [https://kojiki.kokugakuin.ac.jp/shinmei/ayakashikonenokami/ Ay